<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>VeriDrive Mockup</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --blue: #0066cc;
      --blue-dark: #2997ff;
      --ink: #1d1d1f;
      --muted: #7a7a7a;
      --paper: #f5f5f7;
      --dark1: #272729;
      --dark2: #2a2a2c;
      --dark3: #252527;
      --line: #e0e0e0;
      --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22) 3px 5px 30px 0;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: #fff;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: -0.374px;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .global-nav {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0 0 auto;
      z-index: 10;
      height: 44px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 28px;
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: -0.12px;
    }
    .brand { position: absolute; left: 24px; font-weight: 600; }
    .global-nav nav { display: flex; gap: 26px; }

    .sub-nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 44px;
      z-index: 9;
      height: 52px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 24px;
      background: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.82);
      backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    .sub-nav strong { font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: 0.231px; }
    .sub-nav div { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; font-size: 14px; }

    .button, .button-outline, .mini {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 44px;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      transition: transform 160ms ease;
    }
    .button {
      padding: 11px 22px;
      color: #fff;
      background: var(--blue);
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    .button-outline {
      padding: 11px 22px;
      color: var(--blue);
      border: 1px solid var(--blue);
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    .mini {
      min-height: 30px;
      padding: 5px 13px;
      color: #fff;
      background: var(--blue);
    }
    .button:active, .button-outline:active, .mini:active { transform: scale(0.95); }

    main { padding-top: 44px; }
    section {
      min-height: 92vh;
      padding: 80px 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .light { background: #fff; color: var(--ink); }
    .paper { background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); }
    .dark { background: var(--dark1); color: #fff; }
    .dark2 { background: var(--dark2); color: #fff; }
    .dark3 { background: var(--dark3); color: #fff; }

    .copy { width: min(920px, 100%); margin: 0 auto; }
    .eyebrow { margin: 0 0 10px; color: var(--blue); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.47; }
    h1, h2, h3, p { margin-top: 0; }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.07;
      letter-spacing: -0.28px;
    }
    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 4vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }
    h3 {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.24;
    }
    .lead {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      font-size: clamp(21px, 2.4vw, 28px);
      line-height: 1.14;
      letter-spacing: 0.196px;
    }
    .dark .lead, .dark2 .lead, .dark3 .lead { color: #cccccc; }
    .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 18px; }

    .hero { min-height: calc(100vh - 44px); padding-top: 92px; }
    .hero-art {
      position: relative;
      width: min(980px, 95vw);
      min-height: 430px;
      margin-top: 54px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: #f5f5f7;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .vehicle {
      position: absolute;
      width: min(720px, 90%);
      height: 150px;
      bottom: 58px;
      border-radius: 95px 120px 36px 36px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .vehicle:before, .vehicle:after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -34px;
      width: 68px;
      height: 68px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--ink);
    }
    .vehicle:before { left: 110px; }
    .vehicle:after { right: 110px; }
    .phone {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      width: 245px;
      min-height: 410px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 42px;
      background: #09090a;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .phone-notch {
      width: 70px;
      height: 20px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: #1d1d1f;
    }
    .license {
      min-height: 248px;
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: flex-start;
      text-align: left;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #fafafc;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .license small { margin-bottom: auto; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .license strong { color: var(--blue); font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.05; }
    .license p { margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.35; }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 0.9fr) minmax(320px, 1.1fr);
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .split .copy, .split .lead { margin-left: 0; }
    .steps, .cards {
      width: min(760px, 100%);
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .steps li, .card {
      padding: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .steps span {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .steps strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 21px; }
    .steps p, .card p { margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.47; }

    .scan-panel { width: min(720px, 100%); }
    .scan-box {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 280px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #f5f5f7;
    }
    .scan-box .vehicle { bottom: 72px; height: 96px; }
    .scan {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: var(--blue-dark);
      animation: scan 3.8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes scan {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateX(50px); opacity: 0.18; }
      50% { transform: translateX(660px); opacity: 0.9; }
    }
    .status {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }
    .status p {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    .status span { color: #cccccc; }

    .grid {
      width: min(1180px, 100%);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 42px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      min-height: 30px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
      padding: 5px 13px;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      color: var(--blue);
      border: 1px solid var(--blue);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .chain {
      width: min(1120px, 100%);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      margin-top: 44px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }
    .chain span {
      min-height: 112px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.24;
    }
    .trust { min-height: auto; padding: 88px 24px; }
    .trust .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); margin-top: 0; }
    footer {
      min-height: 180px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 48px 24px;
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    footer strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--ink); font-size: 21px; }
    footer p { margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; }

    @media (max-width: 833px) {
      .global-nav nav { display: none; }
      .brand { position: static; }
      .sub-nav div a:not(.mini) { display: none; }
      section { min-height: auto; padding: 64px 20px; }
      .hero { padding-top: 76px; }
      .split, .grid, .trust .grid, .chain { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .split { text-align: center; }
      .split .copy, .split .lead { margin-left: auto; }
      .hero-art { min-height: 360px; }
      .phone { width: 220px; min-height: 380px; }
      footer, .status p { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 419px) {
      h1, h2 { font-size: 28px; }
      .lead { font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; }
      .cta-row, .button, .button-outline { width: 100%; }
      .sub-nav { padding: 0 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="global-nav">
    <a class="brand" href="#top">VeriDrive</a>
    <nav>
      <a href="#verify">ZKP 인증</a>
      <a href="#contract">스마트컨트랙트</a>
      <a href="#return">사고 처리</a>
      <a href="#chain">OmniOne Chain</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <nav class="sub-nav">
    <strong>VeriDrive</strong>
    <div>
      <a href="#flow">프로세스</a>
      <a href="#trust">신뢰 모델</a>
      <a class="mini" href="#demo">목업 보기</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero light">
      <div class="copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Mobile ID. Zero-Knowledge. Smart Contract.</p>
        <h1>믿고 빌리는 개인 간 차량공유.</h1>
        <p class="lead">면허와 나이는 증명하고, 이름과 주민번호는 드러내지 않습니다.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="button" href="#flow">서비스 흐름</a>
          <a class="button-outline" href="#trust">신뢰 구조</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-art" aria-label="VeriDrive hero mockup">
        <div class="vehicle"></div>
        <div class="phone">
          <div class="phone-notch"></div>
          <div class="license">
            <small>Mobile Driver License</small>
            <strong>Verified</strong>
            <p>License valid<br>Age 21+</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="flow" class="dark">
      <div class="copy">
        <h2>개인정보는 감추고, 자격만 증명합니다.</h2>
        <p class="lead">빌리는 사람은 모바일 운전면허증으로 ZKP 인증을 완료합니다. 플랫폼은 “면허 유효”와 “만 21세 이상”만 확인합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="verify" class="paper split">
      <div class="copy">
        <h2>빌리는 사람</h2>
        <p class="lead">인증 후 차량을 고르고, 렌트 신청과 함께 보증금을 스마트컨트랙트에 예치합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li><span>01</span><strong>ZKP 인증</strong><p>면허 유효성과 연령 조건만 증명</p></li>
        <li><span>02</span><strong>차량 검색</strong><p>조건에 맞는 개인 차량 렌트 신청</p></li>
        <li><span>03</span><strong>보증금 예치</strong><p>계약 전 스마트컨트랙트에 자동 락업</p></li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section id="contract" class="dark2 split">
      <div class="copy">
        <h2>빌려주는 사람</h2>
        <p class="lead">상대의 신원 원문이 아니라 검증 결과만 확인합니다. 출발 전 차량 상태는 AI 분석으로 체인에 기록됩니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scan-panel">
        <div class="scan-box">
          <div class="vehicle"></div>
          <span class="scan"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="status">
          <p><strong>ZKP</strong><span>면허 있음</span></p>
          <p><strong>AI 상태 분석</strong><span>스크래치 없음</span></p>
          <p><strong>계약 조건</strong><span>체인 저장 완료</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="return" class="light">
      <div class="copy">
        <h2>반납도 자동으로, 분쟁은 더 작게.</h2>
        <p class="lead">반납 사진을 다시 분석해 이상이 없으면 보증금은 즉시 반환됩니다. 파손이 감지되면 합의된 위약금만 자동 차감됩니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card"><span class="badge">Clean</span><h3>이상 없음</h3><p>스마트컨트랙트가 보증금을 자동 반환합니다.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><span class="badge">Damage</span><h3>사고·파손 감지</h3><p>사전 합의된 위약금을 차감하고 나머지를 반환합니다.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><span class="badge">Record</span><h3>영구 기록</h3><p>거래 이력은 OmniOne Chain에 남습니다.</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="chain" class="dark3">
      <div class="copy">
        <h2>신뢰의 기록은 한 번만 쓰입니다.</h2>
        <p class="lead">인증 결과, 차량 상태, 계약 조건, 보증금 집행 이력을 하나의 검증 가능한 타임라인으로 정리합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="chain">
        <span>Identity Proof</span>
        <span>Deposit Locked</span>
        <span>AI Snapshot</span>
        <span>Return Decision</span>
        <span>Final Settlement</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="trust" class="paper trust">
      <h2>플랫폼 신뢰 모델</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card"><h3>ZKP Privacy</h3><p>민감정보 노출 없이 렌트 자격만 검증합니다.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Smart Escrow</h3><p>보증금 예치와 반환 조건을 계약 코드로 고정합니다.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>AI Evidence</h3><p>출발·반납 사진 분석 결과를 분쟁 근거로 남깁니다.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>On-chain Audit</h3><p>거래 이력을 OmniOne Chain에 검증 가능하게 기록합니다.</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer id="demo">
    <div>
      <strong>VeriDrive</strong>
      <p>모바일 신분증 기반 P2P 차량공유 신뢰 플랫폼 목업</p>
    </div>
    <a class="button" href="#top">맨 위로</a>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
